186
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:30,700
Number 12, pristine.

187
00:09:30,700 --> 00:09:33,700
Pristine, oh, I love this word.

188
00:09:33,700 --> 00:09:35,700
It's so expressive.

189
00:09:35,700 --> 00:09:39,860
It means fresh and clean, as if new.

190
00:09:39,860 --> 00:09:41,980
Her house was pristine.

191
00:09:41,980 --> 00:09:44,390
It's another that my mother uses a lot.

192
00:09:44,390 --> 00:09:49,310
Her house is always pristine,
