194
00:09:52,020 --> 00:09:55,720
Number 13 is surreptitiously.

195
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:57,620
Surreptitiously.

196
00:09:57,620 --> 00:10:00,800
It means in a quick or secret way

197
00:10:00,800 --> 00:10:02,870
so that people don't notice.

198
00:10:02,870 --> 00:10:03,720
