201
00:10:11,920 --> 00:10:14,770
Number 14 is dulcet.

202
00:10:14,770 --> 00:10:16,060
Dulcet.

203
00:10:16,060 --> 00:10:19,410
This means sounding sweet or pleasant

204
00:10:19,410 --> 00:10:22,420
